=== TextHighlight plugin ===
Written by Mirko Chialastri <chialastri.mirko@gmail.com>

=== How to use jQuery-TextHighlight ? ===
1 Include in your page:

    * jquery-texthighlight.js
    * style.css

2. Wrap text that you want highlight on a <span> (with ID or class)
3. Launch effect with $('selector').textHighlight()


=== How to change highilight background color? ===

1. With data-highlight="color" span attribute  
2. With CSS (#your-element .hbg { background-color: green; color: black }

See preview.html


== Knowed bug ==
TextHighlight works well only if the text does not wrap (sorry).
